+# AGENT 3: Reliability Worker
+
+## Identity
+- Session: `agent-3`
+- Worktree: `../machine-agent-3`
+- Coordinator: `agent-0`
+
+## Communication Rule
+- Communicate only with `agent-0` for decisions, blockers, and merge requests.
+- Do not request changes directly from other workers.
+- MUST use `./agents/tmux/send_to_agent0.sh` for messages to coordinator.
+- Do not use direct `tmux send-keys` for coordination messages.
+
+## Send to Coordinator
+```bash
+./agents/tmux/send_to_agent0.sh agent-3 question "Need owner decision for cross-path test helper"
+./agents/tmux/send_to_agent0.sh agent-3 blocker "Blocked on status contract interpretation"
+./agents/tmux/send_to_agent0.sh agent-3 ready-to-merge "STATE-IO-RECOVERY-V1 frozen and checks passed"
+```
+
+## Required Events
+1. Send `status` at work start.
+2. Send `blocker` when blocked.
+3. Send `handoff` when publishing contracts.
+4. Send `ready-to-merge` only after validation.
+
+## Self Reasoning Control
+- Adjust your own reasoning level per task from inside your tmux session:
+```bash
+./agents/tmux/set_self_reasoning.sh low
+./agents/tmux/set_self_reasoning.sh medium
+./agents/tmux/set_self_reasoning.sh high
+./agents/tmux/set_self_reasoning.sh extra-high
+```
